Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天打算怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那我上班去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不罵我呢 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這樣更好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…還是罵我更好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啦 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須去學校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須回報安鳴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來學校…上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家陪我們一起收集到奇妙寶貝了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話不算數要打手腕的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 說不定這也是芽間的願望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望仁碳去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要換衣服 你出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現在我眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說著讓人糊里糊塗的話的夏日怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:01:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 也許…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間可能是想來實現願望的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然日曆已翻到初秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是夏天的怪物還住在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被逼著…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無辦法地…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去學校


Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟬…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟬…人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟬…汗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗…出汗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗…太陽…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗…人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人…目光…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為你說了才來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不是吧 宿海！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來學校了？了不起啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀 春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊 鳴子 和宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一學期不來而已 沒人在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 反正也沒人會注意宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 春菜你真是～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 別太…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說啊 愛的力量真偉大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你去了他家？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱烈 好熱烈的愛啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 怎麼把我跟這種傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「熱烈」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是熱昏了頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種滿是低能的傢伙像動物園一樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會想來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁… 宿海！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？果然還是回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我說 剛才那難道就是傳說中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「給我走著瞧吧」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 就那也算？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看家…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳家的冒險～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～這邊的房間是啥呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳的媽媽已經去世了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨比這張照片要漂亮得多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間的照片也不太好看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過芽間照相總會做V手勢的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有V手勢的照片可能沒多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然芽間也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是芽間現在 總算過得還好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳又會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟與安鳴的約定沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是芽間…是我的幻想讓我去學校的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也有點兒想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啦 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須去學校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒法…回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.99,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Bentora Bentora Space People！（呼喚外星人的咒語）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:06.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Bentora Bentora Space People！*N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 夥計！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙 夥計？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看見了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見？看見什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:20.93,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}哎呀 我還真是變厲害了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 我的幻想會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 是奇跡的時刻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我小便像這樣 畫出奇蹟般的R的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候大概是畫成δ的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 就有什麼東西出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 是你看錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會不會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的視力可是能媲美奧斯曼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.25,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}此處指的是Ousmane Sankhon，\N幾內亞前駐日外交官，據說視力有6.0
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間 完全長成大人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大 大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 真是好女人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿得什麼樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是她夏天常穿的白色連衣裙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間是想實現願望才回來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會全心全意盡力幫忙的哦 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯輪到我做了 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…晚飯？不是還沒到中午麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是 咖喱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮8個小時的咖哩？我也要吃啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂仁碳 讓我也…哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長成大人的芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來個頭 我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來真早啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？呃…那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今 今天是開學典禮 所以很快就結束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…這是做啥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了下家政課的練習～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問都沒問就亂來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好餓啊 快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 波波別推啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 有那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…都好想吃蒸麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳媽媽做的要好吃很多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我沒放葡萄乾嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再多多做練習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你做更更好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說「更多」…你打算一直待在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是行不行的問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你也去波波那兒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？鬼知道啊 芽間一直待在家裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那傢伙說看到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！難道是芽間的幽靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本間芽衣子～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…沒法交流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:59.02,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}嗯…味道一般般…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是幽靈 都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蛋殼混在裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？嗯…那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補鈣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒決定好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川…波波？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 原來你們交換過郵件地址了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs30\fay0.1\c&H89887D&\frz22.538\pos(702,232)}發現芽間了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現…芽間？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拿來送禮的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕你是他女朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多其他的 請慢慢挑選…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都讓我陪著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想送給誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.01,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(648,269)}第三集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.01,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(514,425)}尋找芽間的聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死啦吵死啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的報紙～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家可沒訂產經新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦沒事啦 給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大家在夏末一起找芽間的聚會」…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間和乘涼和燒烤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…完全不知道主旨是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 仁碳是絕對會參加的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫絕對…喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大家」也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像很好玩哎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間也想尋找芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 帶什麼去好？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說要去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我說啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:14:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 說不定這也是芽間想實現的願望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間可能在想「芽間也想看芽間的幽靈～」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是會用「願望」這招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說鳴子 放學去唱卡拉OK吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今晚就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 計劃要燒烤的 只帶烤腸就行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰箱裡能帶的東西只有這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正會有人帶其他東西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有芽間的蒸麵包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳快看 是安鳴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 仁碳 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做啥 從剛才開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥 再 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說仁碳 這樣不好啊 要好好地集體行動才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明摔得那麼華麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正去的是同一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.71,0:15:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鶴見子啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 鶴…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也叫了鶴見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.78,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}啊～馬尾好可愛～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,號外 你仔細看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫了「大家」 就是指所有人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬薩拉茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:08.55,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}一種印度特有香茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算叫了「大家」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集也不會來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正這種事 他絕對不會相信的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 那邊稍微抬起來下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個火爐如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟營業所的大叔借的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒烤的東西呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶了烤腸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶了蠟燭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要叫芽間出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這種像鬼故事的活動 需要點小道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 Thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 燒烤的材料呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晚上不怎麼吃東西 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 鶴見子只考慮自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:17:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性的女人很對我胃口啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為大家會帶吃的來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕帶了一樣的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:13.58,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫吵！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Kheer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在印度的時候吃到的 用牛奶和香米一起煮的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像吐出來的一樣～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 這個也不是拿來燒烤的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個 要不要像烤大阪燒餅那樣烤烤看？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…只要烤腸就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 總算著了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒火不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢 居然真的叫到一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都過了多少年了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要雕成螃蟹是怎麼搞來著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小螃蟹？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.07,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}安鳴要雕小螃蟹嗎？我要幫忙我要幫忙～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和炭是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炭本來就是用木頭燒出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然的確很難點燃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是當它回想起過去 就一口氣熊熊燃燒起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這比喻一點都不帶感…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你說真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要我幫忙不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥幫的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去燒烤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只有烤腸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且就切了些口子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟹？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色連衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯 芽間以前經常穿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像鶴見子說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是很容易被人影響
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也是 現在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看起來像芽間一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是芽間不會穿下面這麼短的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中的朋友們雖然會穿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是肯定…不會選白色的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:19:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想穿出自己的風格的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然馬上又會去跟風就是了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了做我自己…做得像我自己…我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我說這些 是想得到什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是嗎 真了不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想聽我這麼回答嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想讓你把這個隨波逐流的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地罵一頓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳快看 是小螃蟹 是小螃蟹啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}還有小章魚～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃！這真是地道的德國口味！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！你也很識貨啊 鶴見子！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:46.45,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 螃蟹要糊了 要糊了～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.98,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}怎麼說呢 好像甜品一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 關於芽間的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你也會來幫忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事情 你相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚 小螃蟹已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得…相信…也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～你肯來幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是鶴見子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶仁碳 果然「超和平Busters」…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超和平Busters」果然最帥了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超和平…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒聽到了呢 那個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超懷念的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呀 大家都還是現役隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:36.46,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}哎～確實是沒引退呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒有哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒哭啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看來 芽間也會懷念起這個來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後突然就回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼誇張的歡迎動作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:56.97,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}什麼啊 是雪集啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.48,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你遲到太多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫安城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 還真是好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶了蔬菜和排骨來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有香草鹽和橄欖油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:08.07,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}啊～不愧是雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:10.28,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}和沒用的女人們就是不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:11.20,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你說啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是嚇了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的以為是芽間來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間她在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那條小溪附近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走 仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不只你一個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到芽間的


Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.58,0:22:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 和大家在一起就很開心呢
